text: High Plains Drifter is a 1973 American western movie directed by Clint Eastwood (who also stars) and also starring Verna Bloom, Mariana Hill, Billy Curtis, Mitch Ryan, Jack Ging, Ted Hartley, Anthony James, Robert Donner, Buddy Van Horn. It was distributed by Universal Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1973 movies Category:1970s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Clint Eastwood
